title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Cancun
description:
In this addon spotlight we are going to look at both Cancun International airport (MMUM) and the hotel strip from Cancun. The last one is a complete new addon which has been released recently which adds multiple hotels to the hotel strip near Cancun city. After visiting the hotel strip we will continue our flight to Cancun International Airport which also received an update.

If you want to give the airport a try yourself you can download it from the site below: 
https://flightsim.to/file/17796/mmun-cancun-international-airport

If you also want to add the hotels, download the required files from the link below:
https://flightsim.to/file/19338/cancun-zona-hotelera
